    <item>
      <title>DESTRUCTION DARIUS</title>
      <link>http://guoboism.github.io/collect/destructionRadius/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Dec 2015 08:35:50 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://guoboism.github.io/collect/destructionRadius/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd6.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd4.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://guoboism.github.io/images/dd5.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this game, you drop bombs to clear a way to reach the target place.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But not only the explosion will kill you, the after-effect of the blocks are dangerous too!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The concrete block will break into pieces that would fall around;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the wooden blocks contains  fragements bouncing fast between walls;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and there are boxes that would spawn more bombs when exploded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The game combines puzzle (how to bomb) and action (evade dangerouse stuff).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bomb is always a duo-effect (both good and bad) action in games, and the introduction of various blocks and their after effects multiplies the possibilities dramatic consequences.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gamejolt.com/games/destruction-darius/80097&#34;&gt;GameJolt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
