&lt;p&gt;In this game you reach a target place and then the island would rise a bit from water.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Control scheme, left and right to move left and right, double tap to jump to move in that direction.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As ld34 entry, this game explores (successfully) adding more action under the two-button-limitation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It also use the grow theme uniquely with terrain gradually emerge from water generating more gameplay (or change existing gameplay).&lt;/p&gt;

